OL,3,CFamily of teen who died in River Tame
OL,4,Csays they 'will be forever heartbroken'
OL,6,FThe family of a teenage girl who died
OL,7,Fin a river near Kingsbury Water Park
OL,8,Fsay they are "completely devastated
OL,9,Fand will be forever heartbroken".
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,12,FRiver Tame, near Bodymoor Heath Lane,
OL,13,Fjust before 6.10pm on Monday, May 25,
OL,14,Fafter reports a girl had got into
OL,15,Fdifficulty.
OL,17,FWarwickshire Police have confirmed
OL,18,Fthat, after around an hour of
OL,19,Fsearches, the body of 16-year-old
OL,20,FLillianna Tomlinson was recovered from
OL,21,Fthe river.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
