OL,3,CFamily of teen who died in River Tame
OL,4,Csays they 'will be forever heartbroken'
OL,6,FThe force says specially-trained
OL,7,Fofficers are continuing to support her
OL,8,Ffamily.
OL,10,FIn a statement from the family
OL,11,Freleased through the police, it reads:
OL,12,F"We're deeply saddened to be writing
OL,13,Fthat Lillianna's life has been taken
OL,14,Fin the most tragic way.
OL,16,F"Our family is completely devastated
OL,17,Fand will be forever heartbroken.
